Abstract Advisory Information:
==============================
The vulnerability laboratory core research team discovered a persistent cross site vulnerability in the official Weblication CMS Core & Grid v12.006.024 CMS.



Vulnerability Disclosure Timeline:
==================================
2018-02-21: Public Disclosure (Vulnerability Laboratory)


Discovery Status:
=================
Published


Affected Product(s):
====================

Exploitation Technique:
=======================
Remote


